🔥 Features
✅ Simple & easy-to-use interface 🖥
✅ Supports 7 planets 🌎
✅ Accurate weight conversion ⚖
✅ Error handling for incorrect inputs ❌

💡 Notes
The program only accepts planets with the first letter capitalized (e.g., Mars instead of mars).

We assume input weight is in kilograms (kg).

